274
00:20:37,060 --> 00:20:39,360
Thanks.

275
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:43,790
I was fifteen years old when I joined Ling Long. Just like then, I followed my teachers

276
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:48,080
