337
00:26:11,980 --> 00:26:13,890
She won't be back again.

338
00:26:15,140 --> 00:26:17,350
Cai Hong, seriously.

339
00:26:17,350 --> 00:26:21,410
She left without telling me first.

340
00:26:22,530 --> 00:26:24,820
It's such a pity.

341
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:28,830
