354
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:09,670
Pull it up.

355
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:18,890
So beautiful.

356
00:28:18,890 --> 00:28:22,590
That's great.

357
00:28:25,490 --> 00:28:28,710
So beautiful.

358
00:28:28,710 --> 00:28:30,930
