372
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:40,060
I want to bet on Rong Da. Rong Da looks good. Although I have not won at the auction before,

373
00:29:40,060 --> 00:29:41,650
I won't be wrong this time.

374
00:29:41,650 --> 00:29:43,320
Come. Do you have any money?

375
00:29:43,320 --> 00:29:45,340
My bet is for ten dollars.

376
00:29:45,340 --> 00:29:48,080
